[SqlMethod(IsDeterministic = true, IsPrecise = false)]
public SqlDouble STArea()
{
	if (this.IsNull)
	{
		return SqlDouble.Null;
	}
	this.ThrowIfInvalid();
	return Microsoft.SqlServer.Types.GLNativeMethods.GeodeticArea(this.GeoData, this.GetEllipsoidParameters());
}



// Microsoft.SqlServer.Types.GLNativeMethods
public static double GeodeticArea(Microsoft.SqlServer.Types.GeoData g, Microsoft.SqlServer.Types.EllipsoidParameters ellipsoidParameters)
{
	using (Microsoft.SqlServer.Types.GeoDataPinner geoDataPinner = new Microsoft.SqlServer.Types.GeoDataPinner())
	{
		double result = default(double);
		Microsoft.SqlServer.Types.GLNativeMethods.ThrowExceptionForHr(Microsoft.SqlServer.Types.GLNativeMethods.GeodeticArea(geoDataPinner.Pin(g), ellipsoidParameters, out result));
		return result;
	}
}
